# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
#
# <body>
#
# Documentation Requirements:
# - [ ] Documentation created (if required by change type/scope)
# - [ ] Documentation reviewed and approved
# - [ ] Historical context preserved in docs/history/
# - [ ] Sequential number assigned (use ./scripts/create-doc.ps1)
#
# <footer>
#
# Types: feat, fix, docs, style, refactor, perf, test, build, ci, chore, revert
# Scopes: chain, app, story-generator, infra, workspace, deps
#
# Documentation Required For:
# - feat: Major features (>5 projects or >10k lines)
# - fix: Complex or critical bug resolutions
# - refactor: Major structural changes
# - perf: Significant performance optimizations
#
# Example: build(workspace): add pnpm lockfile for dependency management
#
# Documentation Command: ./scripts/create-doc.ps1 <type> <title> <pr>

